com.facebook.buck.rules.coercer

Class AppleSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.coercer.AppleSource

  • public class AppleSource
extends Object
    Simple type representing an iOS or OS X source entry, which can be either:
    • A SourcePath, or
    • A SourcePath plus compiler flags, or
    • A "source group" (a group name and one or more AppleSource objects)
